item.title: Clean Up Your Digital Life: How I Found 1929 Fully Identical Images, Dark, Bright and Blurry Shots in Minutes, For Free.
item.description: âœ… Motivation In today’s world of selfies and Instagram, we all take tons of photos on our phones, cameras, and other gadgets. But let’s be real, it’s easy for our photo collections to become a chaotic mess, making it impossible to find that one special memory. I mean, I’ve got gigabytes of photos on my Google Photo app filled with dark shots, overly exposed shots, blurry shots, and tons of duplicate stills.
